BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

a. 
The scale factor is [`[$k]`]. Because this [$flip] less than 0, the graph  [$flip] flipped across the [`x`]-axis. 

[@ image(insertGraph($gr), width=>$xp, height=>$yp, tex_size=>700) @]*




